frames.caption: A young child in a light blue dress holds a large dandelion puff high above her head as she walks through a vibrant meadow. The scene is bathed in warm sunlight, with colorful flowers and lush greenery surrounding her. A rainbow arcs across the sky, adding a touch of magic to the idyllic landscape.
frames.description: The scene depicts a picturesque meadow during a sunny day, where a child is joyfully exploring nature. The setting is serene and enchanting, with a rainbow and a variety of blooming flowers enhancing the natural beauty.
